author: Russell Brand
description:
Go to https://TryFum.com/RUSSELLBRAND or scan the QR code and use code RUSSELLBRAND to get your free FÜM Topper when you order your Journey Pack today!

Free speech is under threat in the UK like never before. In this episode, I unpack new legislation targeting protestors and pro-Palestinian groups, explore the growing alliance between liberal politics and authoritarian control, and examine how laws once aimed at terrorism are now being used to silence dissent. From George Monbiot's warnings to the potential rise of autonomous weapons and facial recognition, we’re staring down a future where protest could mean prison. But is there another way?
